1. DOWNLOAD ZIP FILE
2. EXTRACT THE ZIP FILE
3. NOW OPEN YOUR C DRIVE
4. OPEN YOUR USERS FOLDER
5. THEN OPEN ADMIN FOLDER
6. NOW SEARCH ANDROID PROJECTS FOLDER
7. PASTE THE FOLDER HERE
8. NOW OPEN ANDROID STUDIO
9. OPEN THAT FILE IN ANDROID STUDIO
10. WHEN YOU OPEN THIS FOLDER IN ANDROID STUDIO THEN GRADLE WILL BUILD AND PLUGIN WILL ALSO DOWNLOAD

NOTE:- YOU NEED INTERNET CONNECTION FOR PLUGIN DOWNLOADS
